com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.nameServerSet

Class NameServerSetListResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.nameServerSet.NameServerSetListResponse

  • public class NameServerSetListResponse
extends Object
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a NameServerSetListCommand, returning the list of retrieved NameServerSetRecords. A NameServer Set represents a logical entity of the DNSAPI architecture, to link an Account with a NameServer Interface Set, through the configuration of the Name Server names that will be provided to the Account's Zones.
    Author:
    Chris Wright
